    <title>learn-git</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/04/03/learn-git/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/04/03/learn-git/</id>
    <published>2019-04-03T08:57:09.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-04-03T09:15:21.920Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="导读"><a href="#导读" class="headerlink" title="导读"></a>导读</h2><p>git配置及常用命令<br><a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="git设置友链1"><a href="#git设置友链1" class="headerlink" title="git设置友链1"></a>git设置<a href="https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000016269686" target="_blank" rel="noopener">友链1</a></h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;xxx&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;xxx&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --list</span><br><span class="line">git config --global --unset user.name</span><br><span class="line">git config --global --unset user.email</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;xxx&quot;</span><br><span class="line">ssh-add ~/.ssh/&lt;github_id_rsa&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">touch config</span><br><span class="line">Host github </span><br><span class="line">HostName github.com </span><br><span class="line">User xxxx </span><br><span class="line">IdentityFile ~/.ssh/&lt;github_id_rsa&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="分支友链2"><a href="#分支友链2" class="headerlink" title="分支友链2"></a>分支<a href="https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/wiki/0013739516305929606dd18361248578c67b8067c8c017b000" target="_blank" rel="noopener">友链2</a></h2><ul><li>查看所有分支(本地+远端) <code>git branch -a</code></li><li>创建分支 <code>git branch &lt;name&gt;</code></li><li>切换分支 <code>git checkout &lt;name&gt;</code></li><li>创建➕切换分支 <code>git checkout -b &lt;name&gt;</code></li><li>合并分支到当前分支 <code>git merge &lt;name&gt;</code>   <code>git merge --no-ff -m &quot;xxx&quot;&lt;name&gt;</code></li><li>取远端分支到本地一个新分支 <code>git checkout -b &lt;name&gt; origin/&lt;name&gt;</code></li><li>删除本地分支 <code>git branch -d &lt;name&gt;</code>   <code>git branch -D &lt;name&gt;</code></li></ul><h2 id="查看历史"><a href="#查看历史" class="headerlink" title="查看历史"></a>查看历史</h2><ul><li><code>git log --graph --pretty=format:&#39;%Cred%h%Creset -%C(yellow)%d%Creset %s %Cgreen(%cr) %C(bold blue)&lt;%an&gt;%Creset&#39; --abbrev-commit</code></li><li><code>git reflog</code></li></ul><h2 id="工作区-暂缓区-分支"><a href="#工作区-暂缓区-分支" class="headerlink" title="工作区 暂缓区 分支"></a>工作区 暂缓区 分支</h2><ul><li>暂存工作区 <code>git stash</code></li><li>恢复 删除暂存的内容 <code>git stash drop</code></li><li><p>查看stash内容 <code>git stash list</code></p></li><li><p>查看远程库信息 <code>git remote</code>    <code>git remote -v</code></p></li><li>本地推送分支 <code>git push origin &lt;name&gt;</code></li><li>删除远端分支 <code>git push origin --delete &lt;name&gt;</code></li><li><code>git pull</code></li><li>本地分支与远程分支关联<code>git branch --set-upstream &lt;name&gt; origin/&lt;name&gt;</code></li><li>本地创建与远程对应的分支 <code>git checkout -b &lt;name&gt; origin/&lt;name&gt;</code></li><li>工作区取消修改<code>git checkout -- &lt;name&gt;</code></li><li>进到指定(HEAD HEAD^…)版本(git commit后) <code>git reset --hard xxxID</code><br>soft参数的话会回退到之前的版本，但是保留当前工作区的修改 hard不保留</li><li>内容提交到暂缓区(git add后)取消修改的内容  1、 <code>git reset HEAD &lt;name&gt;</code>  2、<code>git checkout -- &lt;name&gt;</code></li><li><code>git rm &lt;name&gt;</code>  <code>git commit -m &quot;删除 xxxx&quot;</code></li></ul><h2 id="标签"><a href="#标签" class="headerlink" title="标签"></a>标签</h2> <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git tag -a v0.1 -m &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git tag </span><br><span class="line">git show &lt;name&gt;</span><br><span class="line">git tag -d &lt;name&gt;</span><br><span class="line">推送本地标签 git push origin &lt;tagname&gt;</span><br><span class="line">推送全部为推送的本地标签 git push origin --tags</span><br><span class="line">删除远程标签  git push origin :refs/tags/&lt;tagname&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>]]></content>
    
